reviewText: It just doesn't get any better than Kay Parker in anything, or (nothing at all).
I saw the first movie years ago, this set is great because they cover the main three that include the actress KAY PARKER before in changed to other stories, other actresses.
This movie is an absolute classic!  It is probably my favorite adult film of all time.  Kay Parker is the sexiest woman I have ever seen!  I also loved Dorothy Lemay, Honey Wilder and Aunt Peg!
These discs don't play that well they have aome scratches. I suppose thats what you get when you buy used crap.
